{"tid":574490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"網友大踢爆：名創優品疑用山寨 Lightning 線魚目混珠","createTime":"2018-02-27T12:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T12:33:16.000Z","uid":143760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"26975491518d14dff5706d45a33b3dce65b62834","tid":574490,"uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"自開業以來名創優品 MINISO 一直惹上山寨的爭議，被質疑抄襲「UNIQLO、無印良品、大創」等店鋪的設計風格。不過其商品售價廉價亦吸引不少消費者，而今天則有網友在討論區指摘名創優品連商品都有抄襲的嫌疑，事源網友「如果你知我係邊個」在香港 LIHKG 討論區批評名創優品出售的 Lightning 線材為山寨線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/202233_8a54247b7f3dc7f2a00f525fc2a95d17.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F202233_8a54247b7f3dc7f2a00f525fc2a95d17.png&h=c719ba55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事主：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/574155/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/574155/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/02/27/miniso-fake-lightning/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2Fminiso-fake-lightning%2F&d=WzvR6FohtJpnb6MxcJku9S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6a422592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/02/27/miniso-fake-lightning/</a>"},{"pid":"5a13ec59333956722fccde220056a920ea5ccf95","tid":574490,"uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92e691be3b8776bced7e1ef42757dbded8834bb","tid":574490,"uid":1174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T12:24:44.000Z","msg":"咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a392602b508d3506c7c37426afd39f4e67ef4743","tid":574490,"uid":143760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r